      "text": "Epidemiology and disease burden\nFlavivirus – 4 serotypes \nMost important mosquito-borne viral disease (WHO, 2019)\n4 billion people at risk, 390 million infections, yearly\n96 million symptomatic infections (WHO, 2020)\nEstimated global cost: $39 billion\n A global health concern",
