      },
      "text": "Treatment\nNo dengue-specific antiviral treatment available\n\nPrevention\nDengvaxia® vaccine, Sanofi: approved in several countries for use in dengue-seropositive individuals only\nQDENGA® vaccine, Takeda: recently approved in Indonesia, the European Union and UK for use regardless of previous dengue exposure",
